## UX Notes
- Family member card: blue/indigo color theme to differentiate from rose (woman) and green (asha)
- Family dashboard: simple, clear layout ‚Äî large touch targets, minimal jargon
- Call ASHA Worker button: prominent, orange/amber color, opens a dialog showing ASHA contact details and a "Call Now" link (tel: link)
- Voice fix: language code must match user's selected language so speech recognition works in the right language; show a clear "Microphone permission denied" toast if permission is blocked
